All right. Come, Tofu. Let's eat.

830
01:11:35,624 --> 01:11:37,865
Then Song can take you upstairs.

831
01:11:39,624 --> 01:11:40,905
Come on. Give me a hand.

832
01:11:41,385 --> 01:11:42,305
Here.

833
01:11:42,784 --> 01:11:43,784
Sure.

834
01:11:56,545 --> 01:11:58,425
I'm full. Let's take a walk.

835
01:11:58,905 --> 01:12:02,385
Since you'll be staying here for a while,
you might as well look around.

836
01:12:02,465 --> 01:12:04,585
Come on. I'll show you my favorite place.

837
01:12:05,465 --> 01:12:06,305
Here.

838
01:12:35,345 --> 01:12:37,385
Do you like basketball that much?

839
01:12:41,105 --> 01:12:42,345
It's Neung's stuff.

840
01:12:42,985 --> 01:12:44,065
It's all old.

841
01:12:44,744 --> 01:12:46,025
Mine is in that box.

842
01:12:59,624 --> 01:13:01,585
I would like you to stay in my room,

843
01:13:01,664 --> 01:13:03,105
but it's small and messy.

844
01:13:03,185 --> 01:13:05,025
Stay in Neung's room instead.

845
01:13:05,505 --> 01:13:06,905
You look the same anyway.

846
01:13:22,664 --> 01:13:24,784
It will be like Neung still lives here.

847
01:13:27,865 --> 01:13:30,225
Yes, it will.

848
01:13:34,265 --> 01:13:35,505
Is the room okay?

849
01:13:36,704 --> 01:13:37,545
Yes.

850
01:13:39,465 --> 01:13:40,505
Wait a minute.

851
01:14:11,065 --> 01:14:13,065
Let's play games when you've had a shower.

852
01:14:14,025 --> 01:14:14,905
Okay.

853
01:14:42,784 --> 01:14:45,425
Am I really never
going to see Nut anymore?

854
01:14:55,945 --> 01:14:59,425
TOFU TOFU UPDATED HIS PROFILE PICTURE.

855
01:15:00,425 --> 01:15:05,545
TOFU: I MISS NUT.

856
01:15:48,824 --> 01:15:50,784
Why do I look like you?

857
01:15:55,345 --> 01:15:57,025
Why am I like this?

858
01:15:57,985 --> 01:15:59,425
What happened to me?

859
01:16:07,905 --> 01:16:10,145
I was Nut's teddy bear.

860
01:16:10,704 --> 01:16:12,664
Why did I become your look-alike?

861
01:16:16,545 --> 01:16:17,945
The person Nut loves…

862
01:16:23,585 --> 01:16:25,305
Who did this to me?

863
01:16:40,704 --> 01:16:42,945
Where can I find the answers?

864
01:17:35,824 --> 01:17:37,385
What are you doing, Dad?

865
01:17:43,545 --> 01:17:44,505
What is it?

866
01:17:45,025 --> 01:17:46,345
I saw someone.

867
01:17:46,905 --> 01:17:48,505
They're sneaking around outside.

868
01:17:50,664 --> 01:17:51,704
Is it a burglar?

869
01:17:52,465 --> 01:17:53,345
I don't know.

870
01:18:07,185 --> 01:18:08,025
Dad, wait.

871
01:18:19,465 --> 01:18:20,905
I'll catch the burglar.

872
01:18:20,985 --> 01:18:22,105
What?

873
01:18:22,865 --> 01:18:23,905
It's okay.

874
01:18:32,185 --> 01:18:33,225
Are you leaving?

875
01:18:37,824 --> 01:18:38,985
Did you come to see Tofu?

876
01:18:41,744 --> 01:18:42,744
Come inside.

877
01:18:55,784 --> 01:18:56,784
Thank you.

878
01:18:59,945 --> 01:19:01,145
You're Nut, aren't you?

879
01:19:04,744 --> 01:19:06,305
Song told me.

880
01:19:08,185 --> 01:19:09,145
Yes.

881
01:19:11,824 --> 01:19:13,905
Did you think it through
before coming here?

882
01:19:17,744 --> 01:19:19,985
Although Tofu has lost his memory,

883
01:19:20,704 --> 01:19:23,065
he still has feelings.

884
01:19:24,744 --> 01:19:26,624
You're not just his employer,

885
01:19:26,704 --> 01:19:28,585
and you didn't just save his life.

886
01:19:30,065 --> 01:19:32,225
You're his whole world,

887
01:19:32,985 --> 01:19:35,185
his sanctuary, and something to hang onto.

888
01:19:37,425 --> 01:19:41,225
If you take Tofu back, I only hope

889
01:19:42,345 --> 01:19:46,865
that he will get to stay with you
until his memory returns completely.

890
01:20:03,465 --> 01:20:04,704
Nut!

891
01:20:30,465 --> 01:20:32,185
Let's go home.

892
01:20:53,425 --> 01:20:55,265
Thank you, both of you.

893
01:20:57,545 --> 01:20:58,664
I'll get going now.

894
01:20:59,784 --> 01:21:00,664
Thank you.

895
01:21:03,345 --> 01:21:04,185
Let's go.

896
01:21:06,905 --> 01:21:07,744
Bye.

897
01:21:21,025 --> 01:21:22,425
Did we do the right thing?

898
01:21:22,985 --> 01:21:24,145
I don't know.

899
01:21:24,624 --> 01:21:27,585
But since they miss each other
and they want to stay together,

900
01:21:27,664 --> 01:21:28,865
we have to let them be.

901
01:21:29,985 --> 01:21:33,265
Now, we should go inside
and get some sleep.

902
01:21:33,345 --> 01:21:34,624
Are you sleepy?

903
01:21:34,704 --> 01:21:36,305
-I am.
-Go to bed then.

904
01:21:40,905 --> 01:21:42,385
I thought about the difference

905
01:21:43,545 --> 01:21:45,025
between not having you around,

906
01:21:46,265 --> 01:21:48,585
and having you despite being suspicious.

907
01:21:50,865 --> 01:21:52,505
Did you choose the latter?

908
01:21:53,505 --> 01:21:54,545
No.

909
01:21:55,704 --> 01:21:57,345
I just wanted to follow my heart.

910
01:21:58,425 --> 01:21:59,945
Whatever my heart wants,

911
01:22:00,025 --> 01:22:01,624
I want to let it be.

912
01:22:05,505 --> 01:22:07,065
Right now, I want to be with you.

913
01:22:10,824 --> 01:22:12,905
But I don't know
if I'll get paranoid again.

914
01:22:17,865 --> 01:22:19,465
I don't know what I need to do,

915
01:22:20,185 --> 01:22:22,025
but I want to move forward.

916
01:22:24,065 --> 01:22:25,704
I don't want to leave it hanging.

917
01:22:31,105 --> 01:22:32,624
Please be patient with me.

918
01:22:34,865 --> 01:22:37,025
I promise I'll never kick you out again.

919
01:22:39,065 --> 01:22:40,824
And I'll try not to mention him.

920
01:22:48,505 --> 01:22:50,345
I won't be able to forget him though.

921
01:22:51,985 --> 01:22:53,744
And I won't try to forget him…

922
01:22:57,465 --> 01:22:58,905
because our relationship

923
01:22:59,905 --> 01:23:02,824
is the happiest memory
I have from that time.

924
01:23:17,865 --> 01:23:19,945
But I won't force you to be him,…

925
01:23:21,865 --> 01:23:23,225
because you are you.

926
01:23:25,465 --> 01:23:27,145
He's in the past.

927
01:23:30,025 --> 01:23:31,545
But you're right here

928
01:23:32,505 --> 01:23:33,744
with me.

929
01:23:39,824 --> 01:23:41,225
I promise,

930
01:23:42,744 --> 01:23:44,465
I'll stay with you forever.

931
01:23:52,305 --> 01:23:53,505
Is that all?

932
01:23:55,465 --> 01:23:56,905
What more should I say?

933
01:23:58,704 --> 01:24:00,185
I gave a whole speech,

934
01:24:00,744 --> 01:24:02,105
and that's all you can say?

935
01:24:03,345 --> 01:24:05,265
I must look crazy.

936
01:24:16,065 --> 01:24:17,225
In that case,

937
01:24:18,704 --> 01:24:20,744
I'll try to be good.

938
01:24:22,664 --> 01:24:24,744
I'll be trustworthy,

939
01:24:25,585 --> 01:24:27,865
so that you can trust me,

940
01:24:29,865 --> 01:24:32,225
even though my identity

941
01:24:32,704 --> 01:24:34,624
might not seem so trustworthy.

942
01:24:36,545 --> 01:24:38,345
But everything I've done for you

943
01:24:39,585 --> 01:24:41,945
has always been sincere.

944
01:24:45,225 --> 01:24:46,624
One day,

945
01:24:47,905 --> 01:24:50,664
you'll recognize my sincerity.

946
01:24:52,664 --> 01:24:53,905
I'll prove it.

947
01:24:55,945 --> 01:24:57,185
I promise.

948
01:25:00,465 --> 01:25:02,025
Does that sound good?

949
01:25:04,225 --> 01:25:06,025
Okay. That's good.

950
01:25:07,145 --> 01:25:08,465
You promised.

951
01:25:09,065 --> 01:25:10,345
I'll wait and see.

952
01:25:18,905 --> 01:25:19,905
What now?

953
01:25:20,865 --> 01:25:23,744
This is how we promise.

954
01:25:25,624 --> 01:25:27,385
You're such a baby.

955
01:25:28,505 --> 01:25:31,425
This is how adults make a promise.

956
01:26:08,945 --> 01:26:10,185
Mom is probably asleep.

957
01:26:10,905 --> 01:26:12,225
We can tell her tomorrow.

958
01:26:30,624 --> 01:26:32,105
Welcome home.

959
01:26:41,545 --> 01:26:43,465
Tofu, hurry up.

960
01:26:44,425 --> 01:26:45,345
Okay.

961
01:27:00,585 --> 01:27:01,744
Good night.

962
01:27:02,305 --> 01:27:03,305
Wait.

963
01:27:07,385 --> 01:27:08,864
What is it?

964
01:27:09,585 --> 01:27:10,905
Did you forget something?

965
01:27:12,664 --> 01:27:13,784
What did I forget?

966
01:27:25,305 --> 01:27:26,265
This.

967
01:27:32,905 --> 01:27:34,265
What are you doing?

968
01:27:34,824 --> 01:27:36,505
I'm following your script.

969
01:27:37,864 --> 01:27:38,985
Shall we start?

970
01:27:48,345 --> 01:27:50,145
I'm not really feeling it.

971
01:27:54,065 --> 01:27:55,905
You're so hard to please.

972
01:27:58,225 --> 01:28:00,704
-We can rebuild the mood.
-Sure.

973
01:28:01,545 --> 01:28:03,545
Should we start from the angry part?

974
01:28:06,864 --> 01:28:08,545
Let's skip that.

975
01:28:09,105 --> 01:28:10,185
Then skip to your room.

976
01:28:11,145 --> 01:28:12,345
I'm not in the mood now.

977
01:28:15,105 --> 01:28:16,105
Nut.

978
01:28:16,945 --> 01:28:18,704
I'll skip forward for you.

979
01:28:19,664 --> 01:28:21,345
-Let's start at--
-Go.

980
01:28:22,585 --> 01:28:23,585
I'm going to bed.

981
01:29:05,664 --> 01:29:08,425
You've had him follow me
since we separated.

982
01:29:08,985 --> 01:29:10,425
Are you a psychopath?

983
01:29:10,505 --> 01:29:11,624
Why are you doing this?

984
01:29:12,225 --> 01:29:15,585
I'm doing all this because I love you.

985
01:29:15,664 --> 01:29:18,624
If I can't be happy, then no one will be.

986
01:29:18,704 --> 01:29:20,545
If I wasn't indecisive,

987
01:29:22,105 --> 01:29:23,784
if I had been firm

988
01:29:24,664 --> 01:29:27,425
I wouldn't have made the wrong choice.

989
01:29:27,505 --> 01:29:29,105
She didn't really love him.

990
01:29:29,185 --> 01:29:31,385
I'm just a product of their mistake.

991
01:29:32,425 --> 01:29:33,784
Am I supposed to give up

992
01:29:33,864 --> 01:29:35,824
and be a coward like you?

993
01:29:36,345 --> 01:29:38,385
And behave immorally like you?

994
01:29:38,945 --> 01:29:40,425
-I can't do it.
-Tarn!

995
01:29:42,465 --> 01:29:44,585
I already have plenty of friends.

996
01:29:45,664 --> 01:29:46,784
But now,

997
01:29:47,265 --> 01:29:48,664
I want you.

998
